WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.920
=Episode 20=

01:49.498 --> 01:51.018
That's really amazing.

01:51.018 --> 01:51.377
Really?

01:51.377 --> 01:52.058
I didn't guess.

01:52.058 --> 01:53.337
At the very last second,

01:53.578 --> 01:54.578
band-aid.

01:54.897 --> 01:56.138
How did you figure it out?

01:56.218 --> 01:57.377
Is there a story behind this?

01:57.737 --> 01:59.058
My husband knows me quite well.

01:59.498 --> 02:00.138
The band-aid

02:00.138 --> 02:01.058
was stuck right here.

02:01.808 --> 02:03.633
- Awesome.
- Absolutely.

02:03.778 --> 02:04.457
Sir.

02:06.897 --> 02:07.897
I saw Shen Haoming

02:09.018 --> 02:11.098
and his wife at Yanbo Resort.

02:12.337 --> 02:13.818
They are with the Baraikins.

02:14.418 --> 02:16.337
Looks like we've got competition.

02:16.617 --> 02:17.617
You look into it.

02:18.018 --> 02:19.937
Stop Shen Haoming at all costs

02:20.177 --> 02:21.937
from gaining the Baraikins' favor.

02:22.378 --> 02:23.538
You two are amazing!

02:24.737 --> 02:26.177
How does that Chinese saying go?

02:26.497 --> 02:28.177
A couple

02:28.177 --> 02:29.538
has a connection.

02:30.098 --> 02:30.818
To be precise,

02:30.897 --> 02:34.098
a lovely couple has one heart.

02:34.538 --> 02:36.217
How many times must I remind you?

02:37.378 --> 02:38.337
Tomorrow at the hotel,

02:38.337 --> 02:40.018
there's a folk culture fair.

02:40.018 --> 02:41.858
I'd like to invite you both.

02:42.138 --> 02:42.418
Thanks.

02:42.897 --> 02:43.337
- Okay?
- Sounds good.

02:43.337 --> 02:44.737
We'll be there on time.

02:45.418 --> 02:45.777
Great.

02:46.298 --> 02:47.098
See you tomorrow.

02:48.538 --> 02:50.217
Seeing the two of you

02:50.378 --> 02:51.818
reminds me of my husband and me

02:51.818 --> 02:53.617
when we were just married.

02:54.258 --> 02:55.418
Back when you just married?

02:56.937 --> 02:58.098
We were just

02:58.138 --> 02:59.497
in our twenties.

02:59.858 --> 03:02.057
I was alone in Russia,

03:02.098 --> 03:03.298
working odd jobs

03:03.337 --> 03:04.378
while studying.

03:04.698 --> 03:06.098
No family, no friends.

03:07.657 --> 03:08.457
Then one day,

03:08.538 --> 03:08.937
he walked

03:09.737 --> 03:11.497
into the convenience store
where I worked.

03:11.818 --> 03:12.737
While checking out,

03:12.737 --> 03:13.578
he said,

03:15.098 --> 03:17.217
"You're beauty."

03:17.858 --> 03:18.897
You're beauty?

03:19.258 --> 03:20.777
You're beautiful.

03:21.737 --> 03:23.617
Yes, he said that.

03:24.897 --> 03:26.337
That's when I knew

03:27.057 --> 03:28.298
he was different.

03:29.258 --> 03:30.018
Don't laugh.

03:30.578 --> 03:31.777
I practiced that many times!

03:32.880 --> 03:34.000
Your Chinese is better now.

03:36.298 --> 03:37.777
To your beautiful love story,

03:38.457 --> 03:39.018
let's toast!

03:39.057 --> 03:39.457
Cheers!

03:39.457 --> 03:40.098
Thank you.

04:19.977 --> 04:20.498
Thank you.

04:24.258 --> 04:25.178
I'm wondering

04:26.258 --> 04:28.378
why you're not approaching Mr. Baraikin

04:28.537 --> 04:29.818
through Jinda Group

04:30.018 --> 04:30.857
formally?

04:31.417 --> 04:32.417
Why go to all this

04:32.417 --> 04:33.537
to get close to him?

04:35.457 --> 04:36.977
Is the company in trouble?

04:41.417 --> 04:42.258
The truth is,

04:42.258 --> 04:43.897
my dad doesn't trust me at the company.

04:45.818 --> 04:47.537
Those old men on the board

04:48.657 --> 04:49.378
all pretend

04:49.618 --> 04:51.178
to humor me.

04:51.537 --> 04:52.297
Moreover,

04:52.738 --> 04:54.138
Jinda Group's

04:54.138 --> 04:55.217
overseas managers

04:56.738 --> 04:57.738
were incompetent,

04:57.857 --> 04:59.058
so international expansion

04:59.097 --> 05:00.578
has always been our weak spot.

05:02.378 --> 05:03.618
I have neither

05:04.217 --> 05:06.777
management authority
over international operations

05:06.897 --> 05:07.537
nor a seat

05:08.417 --> 05:09.578
on the board.

05:09.818 --> 05:11.217
My dad always doubts my decisions.

05:11.818 --> 05:13.138
Trying to approach Mr. Baraikin

05:13.977 --> 05:16.097
unofficially under the company name

05:17.897 --> 05:18.818
would be

05:18.818 --> 05:20.297
completely improper.

05:21.818 --> 05:22.297
So,

05:22.378 --> 05:23.857
during his stay in China,

05:25.457 --> 05:26.578
I must convince him

05:26.738 --> 05:27.378
to add Jinda

05:28.417 --> 05:29.258
to his list

05:29.578 --> 05:31.018
of potential partners.

05:32.258 --> 05:33.537
Once we secure this deal,

05:34.378 --> 05:36.297
I'll earn my board seat.

05:40.618 --> 05:42.097
You failed to have a board seat?

05:43.058 --> 05:45.217
My dad voted against it.

05:45.537 --> 05:46.178
Why?

05:48.378 --> 05:49.977
Not the first time he's rejected me.

05:52.657 --> 05:53.857
I had a child out of wedlock.

05:54.657 --> 05:55.178
And also,

05:55.337 --> 05:56.457
I decided on bring Haochen

05:56.618 --> 05:57.698
home to raise him.

05:58.698 --> 06:00.537
That caused disagreements with him.

06:01.618 --> 06:02.738
Since then,

06:04.217 --> 06:05.618
he's never fully trusted me again.

06:23.537 --> 06:24.337
How's Haochen

06:25.498 --> 06:26.297
doing lately?

06:28.698 --> 06:29.738
He is not

06:31.058 --> 06:32.058
mischievous anymore.

06:32.618 --> 06:33.417
He's more sensible.

06:50.217 --> 06:51.818
Would you tell me

06:52.457 --> 06:54.097
about Haochen's biological mother?

07:07.578 --> 07:08.857
It's okay if you don't want to.

07:15.618 --> 07:17.897
Actually, I discovered her pregnancy

07:20.498 --> 07:22.378
two months after I broke up with her.

07:23.498 --> 07:25.698
I remember it was pouring rain that day.

07:26.657 --> 07:27.857
She came to find me.

07:49.217 --> 07:49.897
Have some water.

07:50.337 --> 07:50.938
Thanks.

08:03.378 --> 08:04.297
Why did you come here?

08:14.178 --> 08:14.897
I'm pregnant.

08:17.297 --> 08:18.018
The baby is yours.

08:19.977 --> 08:21.378
I planned to get an abortion,

08:21.378 --> 08:22.018
but the doctor

08:23.417 --> 08:24.857
said if I terminated this pregnancy,

08:25.378 --> 08:26.618
I'd never conceive again.

08:27.777 --> 08:29.618
We broke up months ago.

08:31.258 --> 08:31.938
Are you kidding?

08:32.978 --> 08:34.577
You were the only one I'd been with.

08:40.218 --> 08:40.817
Haoming,

08:41.297 --> 08:42.138
don't worry.

08:42.577 --> 08:44.498
I'm just here to inform you

08:45.417 --> 08:46.498
that you have a child.

08:47.338 --> 08:48.537
Someday I'll tell our child

08:48.537 --> 08:49.378
he has a father.

08:50.992 --> 08:52.496
I'm not asking you to be responsible.

08:53.657 --> 08:54.777
I'll raise the baby alone.

08:56.458 --> 08:56.978
Alright,

08:57.057 --> 08:57.738
that's all.

09:00.458 --> 09:01.577
I'll leave soon.

09:02.378 --> 09:03.458
Take care, Haoming.

09:04.258 --> 09:04.978
Don't worry.

09:05.018 --> 09:05.897
I've decided.

09:06.738 --> 09:07.738
Since I'm keeping it,

09:07.738 --> 09:08.978
I can't stay in the dorm.

09:09.338 --> 09:10.458
I can't tell my dad either,

09:10.458 --> 09:11.618
or he'd literally kill me.

09:12.218 --> 09:12.817
So,

09:12.978 --> 09:14.697
I'll go to Manchester.

09:14.978 --> 09:16.618
I have a friend there
and will stay there.

09:16.978 --> 09:17.777
Anyway,

09:18.777 --> 09:19.738
I'll have this baby.

09:23.018 --> 09:23.537
Goodbye.

09:34.018 --> 09:35.338
I stayed with her throughout

09:38.258 --> 09:39.577
until the baby was born.

09:40.897 --> 09:41.618
Unexpectedly,

09:41.937 --> 09:43.378
shortly after Haochen's birth,

09:44.138 --> 09:45.858
Fang Yu went diving with friends,

09:49.218 --> 09:52.537
encountered an ocean current,
and never came back.

10:03.697 --> 10:05.618
DNA tests confirmed you're the father.

10:07.018 --> 10:08.498
I brought Haochen back home.

10:11.218 --> 10:12.777
Perhaps my dad thought this situation

10:14.697 --> 10:15.858
would disrupt the family.

10:21.978 --> 10:22.817
So we declared

10:24.458 --> 10:25.577
Haochen to be my brother.

10:28.817 --> 10:29.618
So your dad

10:29.618 --> 10:31.138
distrusts you

10:33.777 --> 10:35.338
because of this?

10:40.697 --> 10:41.657
Do you resent him?

10:53.697 --> 10:54.937
If you love someone,

10:56.258 --> 10:57.458
you should trust them

10:57.978 --> 10:59.057
and believe their actions

10:59.057 --> 11:00.338
are meant to protect you.

11:04.378 --> 11:06.057
No matter how old we grow,

11:07.618 --> 11:08.897
in our elders' eyes,

11:08.978 --> 11:10.458
we'll always remain children.

11:12.897 --> 11:14.937
But their distrust doesn't equate

11:15.498 --> 11:17.577
to indifference or neglect.

11:22.218 --> 11:22.777
Moreover,

11:23.338 --> 11:25.098
in such a large corporation,

11:26.057 --> 11:27.378
so many eyes

11:27.577 --> 11:28.498
are watching you.

11:29.697 --> 11:30.937
Any minor mistake you make

11:30.978 --> 11:32.417
gets magnified exponentially.

11:32.897 --> 11:34.218
Perhaps your dad believes

11:34.657 --> 11:35.817
being strict with you

11:36.297 --> 11:37.904
is better than others taking advantage.

11:39.657 --> 11:40.697
So I think

11:40.978 --> 11:42.218
his restrictions on you

11:43.858 --> 11:45.378
might stem from his protection.

11:54.177 --> 11:55.297
Are you comforting me?

12:01.417 --> 12:01.978
Yes.

12:04.978 --> 12:06.417
As a partner,

12:07.177 --> 12:08.138
I hope you can always

12:08.138 --> 12:09.458
maintain a good state.

12:10.657 --> 12:11.618
Finalize the cooperation

12:11.618 --> 12:12.858
with Mr. Baraikin.

12:13.858 --> 12:15.577
Then I can receive my payment.

12:17.258 --> 12:18.018
That's it.

12:22.338 --> 12:23.018
Thank you.

12:25.378 --> 12:26.657
I did feel comforted.

12:37.817 --> 12:38.738
Go to bed early.

12:50.697 --> 12:51.978
One more thing.

12:53.177 --> 12:54.098
About the plan

12:54.098 --> 12:54.978
for tomorrow?

12:55.218 --> 12:55.858
No.

12:57.657 --> 12:59.177
Who exactly invested in you?

13:02.177 --> 13:03.618
What's it to you?

13:04.177 --> 13:05.218
Just go to sleep.

13:06.657 --> 13:07.417
Mr. Huang?

13:08.817 --> 13:09.498
Ms. Ma?

13:11.098 --> 13:12.817
Though she has poor judgment,

13:13.218 --> 13:15.537
she's very interested
in emerging industries.

13:18.098 --> 13:18.858
Ms. Sun?

13:21.537 --> 13:22.177
I know

13:22.177 --> 13:23.697
she's always admired you.

13:24.577 --> 13:26.218
But I don't think it's her.

13:27.577 --> 13:28.498
Ms. Meng?

13:30.657 --> 13:31.858
Or my mom?

13:34.177 --> 13:36.018
Just tell me if it's my mom.

13:40.738 --> 13:42.537
We're just business partners now.

13:44.018 --> 13:45.297
Stay out of my affairs.

13:45.858 --> 13:47.098
You have no right to know.

13:47.657 --> 13:49.057
Stop asking these questions.

13:49.498 --> 13:50.817
Remember your place.

13:54.738 --> 13:55.458
Good night.

14:05.338 --> 14:06.177
It's confirmed.

14:07.018 --> 14:08.577
They're in the cooling-off period.

14:09.098 --> 14:10.256
They'll divorce when it ends.

14:11.537 --> 14:12.218
Are you sure?

14:13.417 --> 14:14.338
Pretty sure.

14:15.738 --> 14:16.297
Alright.

14:17.458 --> 14:18.537
I know what to do now.

14:40.738 --> 14:41.697
They're having a fight.

14:43.138 --> 14:45.098
Stop showing off your love.

14:45.738 --> 14:46.618
Drop the act.

14:47.657 --> 14:48.777
True colors revealed.

15:02.417 --> 15:03.657
What's that smell?

15:08.978 --> 15:10.338
Ethnic-style kites.

15:10.817 --> 15:11.777
Quite unique.

15:12.858 --> 15:14.697
Handmade, very beautiful.

15:27.897 --> 15:28.937
This is nice.

15:29.697 --> 15:30.697
This is called

15:31.177 --> 15:32.218
- a sachet.
- Sachet.

15:32.657 --> 15:33.897
It has a pleasant fragrance.

15:34.018 --> 15:35.057
Pick one.

15:35.057 --> 15:36.338
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

15:36.338 --> 15:37.897
The red one looks good.

15:38.218 --> 15:38.618
This one.

15:38.897 --> 15:40.897
Peace and contentment
bring the greatest blessings.

15:40.978 --> 15:41.937
We'll take two of these.

15:41.937 --> 15:42.498
Thank you.

15:43.138 --> 15:43.657
You can

15:43.697 --> 15:44.777
wear it on you

15:44.817 --> 15:46.057
or attach it to your bag.

15:46.138 --> 15:47.218
Or put it in your car.

15:47.458 --> 15:48.417
Since it's a sachet,

15:48.537 --> 15:49.297
the inside

15:49.297 --> 15:50.458
contains herbs.

15:50.458 --> 15:51.057
It's good.

15:51.057 --> 15:51.417
Okay.

15:52.018 --> 15:52.417
Thanks.

15:52.498 --> 15:53.858
This carries different meanings.

15:54.098 --> 15:54.378
Look,

15:55.098 --> 15:55.777
these two

15:55.777 --> 15:57.498
are for you and Mr. Baraikin.

15:57.618 --> 15:59.018
May you always be happy together.

15:59.657 --> 16:01.378
Sweetie, you're too kind.

16:01.378 --> 16:02.177
Thank you.

16:04.338 --> 16:05.657
We need two leaves.

16:05.817 --> 16:06.057
Yes.

16:06.098 --> 16:07.177
Overlap them slightly.

16:08.297 --> 16:08.897
- Like this?
- Yes.

16:09.417 --> 16:10.417
Wrap it up this way

16:10.417 --> 16:11.817
to form a small bowl shape.

16:12.738 --> 16:13.360
Glutinous rice.

16:16.314 --> 16:20.880
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

16:20.880 --> 16:22.992
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

16:23.697 --> 16:26.258
Here is the sweet zongzi you like.

16:27.258 --> 16:29.577
More dates, less bean paste.

16:29.577 --> 16:30.177
Right?

16:30.537 --> 16:31.537
Here you are, honey.

16:34.554 --> 16:39.351
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

16:39.351 --> 16:41.643
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

16:41.643 --> 16:43.997
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

16:43.997 --> 16:50.192
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

16:58.378 --> 16:58.858
Look.

16:59.897 --> 17:01.297
Careful, the filling's spilling.

17:07.418 --> 17:08.218
Just seal it up.

17:13.337 --> 17:14.658
My wife made an open-face zongzi.

17:15.978 --> 17:17.057
See, the teacher made this.

17:17.337 --> 17:17.938
Seal it up.

17:18.018 --> 17:18.857
Open-face zongzi.

17:18.857 --> 17:19.537
Seal it properly.

17:22.458 --> 17:23.698
So sweet.

17:32.857 --> 17:34.938
Hello, room service for 2130.

17:43.297 --> 17:43.817
What?

17:44.097 --> 17:44.857
318, right?

17:45.377 --> 17:46.458
Okay, I'll be right there.

18:07.297 --> 18:08.337
What's this?

18:10.577 --> 18:11.817
This is lip rouge.

18:12.178 --> 18:13.938
Before the invention of tube lipsticks,

18:13.938 --> 18:15.978
in ancient times, it served
as lipstick and blush.

18:16.537 --> 18:18.018
Stored in small containers.

18:18.178 --> 18:18.938
Dip your finger in.

18:19.057 --> 18:20.297
It's convenient and charming.

18:21.258 --> 18:22.857
It comes in various colors. So lovely.

18:24.577 --> 18:25.218
Do you like it?

18:25.458 --> 18:26.137
Beautiful.

18:27.097 --> 18:27.978
And this?

18:29.617 --> 18:31.817
This is called spiral eyebrow pigment,

18:32.418 --> 18:34.978
used for eyebrow grooming
in ancient times.

18:35.178 --> 18:37.018
Its intricate craftsmanship

18:37.137 --> 18:38.617
made it quite valuable.

18:41.458 --> 18:43.218
During the Western Han Dynasty,

18:43.458 --> 18:44.178
an official

18:44.337 --> 18:45.057
named Zhang Chang

18:45.218 --> 18:46.218
drew his wife's eyebrows.

18:47.137 --> 18:47.898
This became known

18:47.898 --> 18:49.537
as a demonstration of affection

18:49.817 --> 18:51.218
between husband and wife.

18:52.097 --> 18:53.418
So, the story of Zhang Chang

18:53.418 --> 18:54.458
drawing eyebrows was made.

18:55.458 --> 18:57.337
A husband doing makeup

18:57.337 --> 18:57.898
for his wife

18:58.018 --> 18:58.777
was considered

18:58.777 --> 19:00.337
an intimate act of love.

19:02.218 --> 19:02.777
Honey,

19:04.537 --> 19:05.978
let's demonstrate for Mr. Baraikin

19:05.978 --> 19:06.658
and his wife,

19:06.777 --> 19:07.498
shall we?

19:12.418 --> 19:13.057
Okay.

19:21.698 --> 19:22.577
She's shy.

20:11.137 --> 20:11.698
Finished.

20:15.418 --> 20:16.137
How does it look?

20:18.337 --> 20:19.498
He is a husband

20:19.498 --> 20:21.258
who can do makeup for his wife.

20:21.738 --> 20:22.857
He must love you very much.

20:24.097 --> 20:25.498
As a Chinese saying goes,

20:25.857 --> 20:27.097
a lovely couple is

20:27.418 --> 20:28.577
intimate and sweet.

20:29.258 --> 20:30.537
It perfectly describes you.

20:31.577 --> 20:32.978
A happy wife

20:33.577 --> 20:34.898
makes a happy life.

20:35.377 --> 20:36.898
Those are your words,

20:37.337 --> 20:38.617
also my motto from now on.

20:39.498 --> 20:40.297
Mr. Baraikin.

20:40.377 --> 20:40.978
Would you

20:41.057 --> 20:41.898
like to try?

20:42.658 --> 20:44.137
I don't think I can do it.

20:45.418 --> 20:45.978
Yan.

20:46.057 --> 20:46.738
Do mine.

20:47.658 --> 20:48.137
Okay.

20:49.137 --> 20:49.857
Let me try.

20:49.978 --> 20:50.577
Go grab coffee.

20:50.577 --> 20:51.617
- Let the ladies enjoy.
- Is this okay?

20:51.738 --> 20:52.857
We'll find our own fun.

20:55.458 --> 20:57.018
May I ask

20:57.377 --> 20:58.898
what you do for a living?

20:59.537 --> 21:00.817
You're so knowledgeable!

21:01.817 --> 21:03.898
I was a news anchor before

21:04.658 --> 21:06.258
and produced food programs.

21:07.458 --> 21:09.418
No wonder you're so versatile!

21:10.817 --> 21:11.577
However,

21:11.577 --> 21:12.698
I've left broadcasting.

21:13.857 --> 21:15.577
With my sister and friends,

21:15.777 --> 21:17.018
we founded

21:17.057 --> 21:18.377
an ethnic-inspired fashion brand.

21:19.577 --> 21:20.738
What I'm wearing

21:21.817 --> 21:22.337
today

21:22.337 --> 21:23.738
is our unreleased sample dress.

21:24.337 --> 21:25.777
No wonder it's exquisite.

21:26.658 --> 21:27.297
You like it?

21:29.337 --> 21:30.178
Wait a moment.

21:32.097 --> 21:34.337
We have brand videos.

21:35.057 --> 21:35.698
Have a look.

21:36.218 --> 21:37.297
Here are more

21:37.337 --> 21:38.498
unreleased designs.

21:38.898 --> 21:39.738
Ethnic-style clothes

21:39.738 --> 21:41.777
aren't just beautiful

21:41.938 --> 21:43.857
but culturally precious.

21:44.097 --> 21:44.777
Today, in cities,

21:44.817 --> 21:46.137
we rarely see them.

21:46.537 --> 21:48.137
That's why we created this brand.

21:49.458 --> 21:50.577
If you'd like,

21:50.658 --> 21:51.337
just choose one.

21:51.418 --> 21:52.057
It's my gift.

21:53.218 --> 21:55.898
How thoughtful!

21:56.018 --> 21:57.698
You're beautiful, kind,

21:57.698 --> 21:58.617
and passionate.

21:58.738 --> 22:00.418
Your husband is lucky to have you.

22:05.898 --> 22:07.137
What does he do?

22:08.938 --> 22:10.498
He is Vice President of Jinda Group

22:10.857 --> 22:11.698
in real estate.

22:12.537 --> 22:13.817
What a coincidence!

22:13.938 --> 22:15.777
My husband is also in real estate.

22:16.698 --> 22:18.018
If my husband knows,

22:18.057 --> 22:18.738
he will

22:18.777 --> 22:20.698
share many common topics
with your husband.

22:23.938 --> 22:25.738
But I made a pact with my husband.

22:26.698 --> 22:27.777
During the vacation,

22:28.418 --> 22:29.377
no work is allowed.

22:30.537 --> 22:31.178
I understand.

22:32.258 --> 22:33.418
Couples

22:33.577 --> 22:35.218
rarely can

22:35.418 --> 22:37.137
get quality time just for themselves.

22:37.938 --> 22:39.258
Let's skip the work talk then.

22:39.418 --> 22:40.137
Just have fun.

22:44.297 --> 22:45.337
Looks great.

22:45.377 --> 22:45.857
Really?

22:45.938 --> 22:46.777
Do you like it?

22:48.377 --> 22:49.498
It's genuinely nice.

22:52.498 --> 22:53.297
Very good.

23:27.938 --> 23:30.097
A lie is a lie indeed.

23:44.057 --> 23:45.698
Are you sure the clothes you chose

23:45.898 --> 23:47.297
will please Mrs. Baraikin?

23:49.057 --> 23:50.097
Absolutely.

23:50.178 --> 23:51.698
Yan Studio's outfits

23:51.777 --> 23:53.018
are perfect for gifting.

24:00.498 --> 24:02.178
I think Mrs. Baraikin has probably

24:02.258 --> 24:03.458
already revealed your identity

24:03.458 --> 24:04.377
to her husband by now.

24:05.337 --> 24:06.418
That's perfect.

24:06.577 --> 24:08.057
We don't have much time left.

24:08.297 --> 24:09.097
They're leaving

24:09.137 --> 24:09.938
tomorrow morning.

24:12.938 --> 24:14.018
But let me remind you.

24:15.297 --> 24:15.817
Since we've

24:15.817 --> 24:17.057
prepared so thoroughly,

24:17.498 --> 24:18.258
we need

24:18.258 --> 24:19.418
to choose the perfect moment.

24:20.978 --> 24:21.898
Don't rush

24:21.898 --> 24:23.218
into business discussions.

24:24.178 --> 24:24.617
Okay.

24:25.018 --> 24:25.617
Thank you.

24:28.137 --> 24:28.978
You don't have to.

24:30.418 --> 24:31.498
I'm following the contract.

24:43.498 --> 24:44.738
Regarding the contract,

24:45.018 --> 24:46.218
I'll make sure to sign it

24:46.898 --> 24:48.218
with Mr. Baraikin soon.

24:49.258 --> 24:49.817
Honey.

24:50.137 --> 24:51.938
Do you like the eyebrows I drew for you?

24:53.018 --> 24:54.178
Of course, I do.

24:54.537 --> 24:56.178
But if you make me angry,

24:56.297 --> 24:57.738
I'll make you do this every day.

25:05.498 --> 25:07.057
You said you were cold yesterday.

25:09.018 --> 25:10.258
Let me get you a blanket.

25:17.738 --> 25:18.258
Thanks.

25:21.377 --> 25:22.337
Ready to go?

25:22.617 --> 25:23.057
Let's go.

25:27.577 --> 25:29.178
This one looks nice.

25:42.097 --> 25:43.018
So,

25:43.018 --> 25:44.297
who was hiding in the wardrobe?

25:45.297 --> 25:46.178
Couldn't see clearly.

25:46.738 --> 25:47.817
He is probably injured.

25:49.938 --> 25:52.018
He might be a corporate spy

25:52.577 --> 25:54.057
targeting the Baraikins.

25:57.218 --> 25:58.137
Why not expose him

25:58.137 --> 25:59.057
directly?

26:00.018 --> 26:01.297
That would alert my opponent.

26:02.458 --> 26:03.777
Just a corporate spy.

26:04.458 --> 26:05.458
Our conversation

26:05.698 --> 26:07.297
didn't reveal any flaws to him.

26:07.898 --> 26:09.337
If we confront him directly,

26:10.218 --> 26:11.377
he might get desperate

26:11.738 --> 26:12.817
and sabotage our plans.

26:13.258 --> 26:14.337
Just go with it for now.

26:17.297 --> 26:19.057
It's ready. For you.

26:19.408 --> 26:21.018
If you like anything else, let me know.

26:21.097 --> 26:22.018
I'll mail it to you.

26:22.377 --> 26:23.898
Thank you.

26:24.698 --> 26:25.938
Shall we have tea together?

26:26.057 --> 26:26.458
Sure.

26:26.658 --> 26:27.097
Let's go.

26:27.577 --> 26:28.377
Thanks.

26:32.738 --> 26:33.698
The sun's gone now.

26:33.698 --> 26:34.537
It's cool.

26:34.738 --> 26:35.178
Sure.

26:35.498 --> 26:35.898
Very nice.

26:35.938 --> 26:38.258
This cultural street is wonderful.

26:38.617 --> 26:39.137
Mr. Baraikin.

26:39.137 --> 26:39.938
You enjoy it here?

26:40.018 --> 26:40.777
Mr. Baraikin.

26:42.577 --> 26:43.018
Steve.

26:43.097 --> 26:43.857
Mr. Baraikin.

26:44.057 --> 26:45.178
What happened to you?

26:45.658 --> 26:46.928
I know you're vacationing here.

26:47.418 --> 26:48.817
I'm here to take a break too.

26:49.377 --> 26:50.297
But this place

26:50.498 --> 26:51.537
isn't welcoming to singles

26:51.537 --> 26:52.258
like me.

26:52.297 --> 26:53.297
I had an accident.

26:53.658 --> 26:54.577
Have a seat.

26:54.738 --> 26:55.377
Careful.

26:55.537 --> 26:56.938
I brought you local specialties

26:57.137 --> 26:58.057
from Jingzhou.

26:58.178 --> 26:59.696
- Hope you'll like them.
- Thank you.

27:05.537 --> 27:06.018
So, have you

27:06.537 --> 27:07.857
been enjoying your time here?

27:08.458 --> 27:09.097
Sure.

27:09.898 --> 27:11.577
My wife and I had a wonderful time.

27:12.577 --> 27:13.297
Most importantly,

27:13.297 --> 27:14.577
we've made some new friends.

27:14.817 --> 27:15.857
They're our neighbors.

27:20.258 --> 27:21.097
Mr. Shen?

27:23.097 --> 27:23.898
Mr. Shen,

27:24.258 --> 27:25.018
nice to meet you.

27:25.377 --> 27:26.577
I'm Steve from Situo.

27:26.938 --> 27:27.698
Do you remember me?

27:28.777 --> 27:29.258
Yes.

27:30.738 --> 27:31.178
Hello.

27:31.178 --> 27:31.698
Hello.

27:32.178 --> 27:32.458
Sit.

27:32.537 --> 27:33.498
Do you know each other?

27:34.458 --> 27:36.377
We met at a summit before

27:36.617 --> 27:37.498
but once.

27:38.218 --> 27:38.857
Mr. Shen

27:38.857 --> 27:39.978
is the heir apparent

27:39.978 --> 27:40.537
of Jinda,

27:40.537 --> 27:41.777
the leading construction group.

27:42.057 --> 27:43.178
He is very famous.

27:44.377 --> 27:45.097
Mr. Shen.

27:45.297 --> 27:46.777
Haven't you introduced yourself yet?

27:47.057 --> 27:47.698
I know.

27:48.137 --> 27:49.498
My wife just told me.

27:49.898 --> 27:51.297
Mr. Shen, glad to meet you.

27:51.777 --> 27:53.297
Surprisingly, we're in the same field.

27:53.978 --> 27:55.057
It's an honor

27:55.137 --> 27:55.938
to meet you.

27:57.018 --> 27:58.057
Seeing you two

27:58.057 --> 27:58.738
vacationing here

27:58.738 --> 27:59.777
is quite surprising to me.

28:00.178 --> 28:02.258
There is a rumor about
you two getting divorced.

28:02.857 --> 28:03.577
Ms. Xu has been

28:03.577 --> 28:04.658
doing live streams, right?

28:10.258 --> 28:11.178
Divorce?

28:12.218 --> 28:13.938
What happened?

28:16.498 --> 28:18.418
People are spreading rumors again.

28:18.617 --> 28:19.938
Don't take those seriously.

28:22.498 --> 28:23.258
My wife

28:23.617 --> 28:25.738
is hands-on with everything.

28:26.018 --> 28:27.898
She does live streams
for market research

28:27.938 --> 28:28.738
on her business.

28:30.337 --> 28:31.178
Her business?

28:31.817 --> 28:32.817
As far as I know,

28:32.817 --> 28:33.498
Ms. Xu

28:33.498 --> 28:35.057
used to be a financial news anchor.

28:35.337 --> 28:36.738
Then she switched to a streamer.

28:37.738 --> 28:38.978
When did you start a business?

28:42.178 --> 28:43.777
After I quit my job,

28:44.297 --> 28:45.297
to start a business,

28:45.337 --> 28:47.617
I entered the live-stream field
to gain experience.

28:48.498 --> 28:50.537
But finding a new direction

28:50.577 --> 28:51.458
is challenging.

28:51.857 --> 28:53.258
Later, I realized it wasn't for me,

28:53.938 --> 28:55.018
so I quit again.

28:55.458 --> 28:56.377
I started Yan Studio.

28:56.418 --> 28:57.537
I told you this afternoon.

28:57.978 --> 28:58.577
Yes.

28:58.698 --> 29:00.418
This outfit is a gift from Ms. Xu.

29:00.418 --> 29:01.297
Chinese-style.

29:01.337 --> 29:02.018
Very beautiful.

29:02.097 --> 29:02.577
Thank you.

29:02.577 --> 29:03.178
Here.

29:03.898 --> 29:05.178
Mr. Baraikin,

29:05.617 --> 29:06.938
if you like,

29:07.377 --> 29:08.698
you can ask my husband.

29:08.738 --> 29:09.577
My husband loves

29:09.577 --> 29:10.857
my studio's clothing.

29:10.978 --> 29:12.057
- Okay.
- Menswear?

29:12.777 --> 29:13.297
Your size

29:13.297 --> 29:14.537
should be similar to mine.

29:14.777 --> 29:15.337
Right?

29:15.617 --> 29:16.097
Plus size?

29:16.097 --> 29:17.057
- I guess.
- Probably.

29:17.577 --> 29:19.057
Mr. Shen and his wife

29:19.057 --> 29:20.297
are indeed very affectionate.

29:20.698 --> 29:21.418
But,

29:22.698 --> 29:23.738
Mr. Baraikin, look.

29:28.137 --> 29:29.698
In Mr. Shen's room,

29:29.978 --> 29:32.258
there's a pillow and blanket
on the living room sofa.

29:33.458 --> 29:34.178
Look,

29:34.418 --> 29:36.938
(toiletries are kept separately.)

29:40.978 --> 29:42.817
Doesn't this seem odd?

29:52.658 --> 29:53.537
The splashing game.

29:54.577 --> 29:56.297
From last night, remember?

29:56.938 --> 29:58.658
When we played that game,

29:58.938 --> 29:59.777
she said

30:00.258 --> 30:02.137
we lacked chemistry.

30:02.698 --> 30:04.617
She took away my chance
to share a bed with her.

30:05.258 --> 30:06.137
I told you.

30:06.297 --> 30:07.617
There's no need to be so serious.

30:08.617 --> 30:10.377
But you played that game very seriously.

30:19.938 --> 30:21.658
How did you get those photos?

30:23.097 --> 30:24.528
If you don't want others to know,

30:25.018 --> 30:26.337
don't do it in the first place.

30:26.857 --> 30:28.978
If you two aren't actually separated,

30:30.418 --> 30:31.178
dare you

30:31.817 --> 30:33.617
take us to see your bedroom?

30:44.698 --> 30:45.777
What's going on?

30:53.617 --> 30:54.057
Well...

31:00.337 --> 31:01.817
It's beautiful!

31:03.418 --> 31:03.898
Well,

31:04.218 --> 31:04.978
this...

31:10.458 --> 31:11.258
This was

31:11.978 --> 31:12.978
prepared for Yan

31:13.137 --> 31:13.978
as a surprise.

31:15.698 --> 31:17.577
They're so romantic!

31:19.018 --> 31:19.617
Sorry,

31:20.777 --> 31:22.817
we ruined your surprise.

31:25.297 --> 31:25.817
It's okay.

31:26.938 --> 31:28.978
I'm happy spending time
with friends too.

31:29.537 --> 31:30.377
Mr. Shen,

31:31.537 --> 31:32.258
I think you have

31:32.258 --> 31:33.377
potential as a magician.

31:34.057 --> 31:35.418
You two look close

31:35.498 --> 31:36.537
outside all the time.

31:39.218 --> 31:40.297
However,

31:42.658 --> 31:44.112
you keep a distance at home, right?

31:52.817 --> 31:53.857
Is there a problem here?

31:55.018 --> 31:56.297
Weren't you fighting?

31:57.777 --> 31:58.658
From your perspective,

31:58.658 --> 31:59.738
this seems like a fight?

32:02.658 --> 32:03.857
I was doing yoga.

32:04.297 --> 32:04.777
What?

32:05.097 --> 32:06.178
My leg wasn't up yet.

32:06.898 --> 32:07.377
See?

32:07.617 --> 32:09.898
If you'd kept filming,
my leg would've been lifted.

32:10.057 --> 32:10.458
Wait.

32:10.498 --> 32:11.664
Honey, what were you doing?

32:12.218 --> 32:12.857
I was...

32:14.337 --> 32:16.057
On a work call with a subordinate.

32:16.218 --> 32:17.377
Sure, you were on a call.

32:17.458 --> 32:18.777
I was criticizing him.

32:19.057 --> 32:20.577
I was kind of emotional.

32:20.777 --> 32:21.840
- Exactly.
- I was yelling.

32:21.938 --> 32:23.097
In this direction, like this.

32:23.097 --> 32:23.418
Sure.

32:23.418 --> 32:23.888
Like this.

32:24.297 --> 32:24.938
I was like this,

32:25.018 --> 32:26.018
lifting my leg.

32:26.057 --> 32:26.738
Exactly the same.

32:26.738 --> 32:27.418
Exactly the same.

32:27.817 --> 32:28.617
Any problem with it?

32:29.178 --> 32:29.978
- Any problem?
- Any problem?

32:32.938 --> 32:33.577
Steve,

32:34.498 --> 32:35.857
what exactly are you trying to do?

32:36.458 --> 32:38.297
You keep secretly photographing us.

32:38.297 --> 32:39.258
That's illegal.

32:39.258 --> 32:41.097
We can call the police.

32:41.178 --> 32:42.377
Right now.

32:49.898 --> 32:50.537
Wait.

32:52.978 --> 32:54.777
This is all a misunderstanding.

32:55.458 --> 32:56.218
You got me wrong.

32:56.658 --> 32:57.658
What misunderstanding?

33:01.178 --> 33:01.857
Let me explain.

33:02.577 --> 33:03.738
This morning when I woke up,

33:03.738 --> 33:04.617
I saw a bird

33:05.377 --> 33:07.218
from my balcony

33:07.738 --> 33:08.938
and tried to photograph it.

33:09.258 --> 33:10.057
But accidentally,

33:10.057 --> 33:10.978
I took a video of you.

33:10.978 --> 33:12.018
It was accidental.

33:12.617 --> 33:13.577
It's a misunderstanding.

33:14.978 --> 33:15.498
Really.

33:16.938 --> 33:17.458
Well,

33:17.938 --> 33:18.498
Mr. Shen,

33:19.097 --> 33:19.857
let me make it up

33:20.018 --> 33:21.137
to you with dinner tonight?

33:22.097 --> 33:23.137
My treat to apologize.

33:31.738 --> 33:33.458
You ruined my husband's surprise.

33:36.218 --> 33:36.658
It's okay.

33:37.097 --> 33:37.857
Maybe next time.

33:45.658 --> 33:46.768
I need to use the restroom.

33:51.938 --> 33:52.658
Ms. Xu.

33:56.337 --> 33:57.178
Ms. Xu,

33:57.857 --> 33:59.817
there's something I've been
wanting to tell you.

34:01.458 --> 34:02.498
I'm a fan of yours.

34:03.938 --> 34:04.658
Really?

34:05.938 --> 34:07.258
I loved your Family Feast

34:07.418 --> 34:08.697
and Financial News.

34:08.898 --> 34:09.778
I mean it.

34:10.458 --> 34:11.818
But you suddenly quit.

34:11.818 --> 34:12.697
I was sad about that.

34:13.257 --> 34:14.378
I've always wanted to ask

34:15.018 --> 34:16.137
if you really quit

34:16.537 --> 34:17.657
just to start a business

34:17.778 --> 34:18.858
back then.

34:18.978 --> 34:21.697
I left specifically
to start my own business.

34:22.338 --> 34:23.338
That's the only reason.

34:23.778 --> 34:24.498
Thank you.

34:24.778 --> 34:26.097
It wasn't due to marital issues?

34:31.177 --> 34:32.177
Don't believe

34:32.177 --> 34:33.137
those baseless rumors.

34:33.978 --> 34:35.137
I told you already.

34:35.298 --> 34:37.137
Rumors gain traction

34:38.018 --> 34:38.938
for good reasons.

34:39.657 --> 34:40.577
I've also heard

34:41.057 --> 34:42.577
you've been scrambling for funding,

34:42.938 --> 34:44.018
but have some problems.

34:44.458 --> 34:46.577
Since you suddenly appear here
with Shen Haoming,

34:48.858 --> 34:50.298
everything makes perfect sense now.

34:51.378 --> 34:52.978
You're likely pretending

34:53.338 --> 34:55.978
to be a happy couple
with Shen Haoming for funds.

35:01.298 --> 35:01.978
I'm sorry.

35:06.818 --> 35:07.498
I'm sorry.

35:08.537 --> 35:09.018
I'm sorry.

35:09.577 --> 35:10.898
I apologize. This is awkward.

35:11.057 --> 35:11.898
My apologies, truly.

35:12.018 --> 35:12.898
It's just...

35:14.617 --> 35:15.577
No offense,

35:15.898 --> 35:17.137
but is it because of this?

35:17.577 --> 35:18.938
Your head injury

35:18.978 --> 35:19.818
makes you

35:20.217 --> 35:21.378
imagine something?

35:24.177 --> 35:25.458
In this world,

35:26.537 --> 35:28.097
no divorced couple

35:28.617 --> 35:30.657
who have gone through bitter separations

35:31.057 --> 35:33.018
and hurt each other

35:33.177 --> 35:34.577
would genuinely wish

35:34.938 --> 35:36.097
for each other's success

35:36.338 --> 35:37.818
in business

35:38.498 --> 35:39.577
and careers.

35:42.778 --> 35:44.097
Divorced partners

35:44.858 --> 35:45.978
become sworn enemies.

35:48.818 --> 35:50.177
If money's your only motive,

35:51.257 --> 35:52.577
we can invest in you.

35:53.657 --> 35:54.778
Whatever he offers,

35:55.217 --> 35:55.938
I'll double it.

35:57.097 --> 35:58.458
I have one small condition.

35:59.057 --> 36:00.418
Publicly expose

36:00.418 --> 36:01.617
your marital fraud

36:03.137 --> 36:05.018
in front of Mr. Baraikin.

36:17.097 --> 36:17.978
Ms. Xu,

36:19.018 --> 36:21.697
why collaborate
with someone you despise?

36:23.577 --> 36:24.737
Refuse if you want.

36:25.657 --> 36:27.697
I'll personally unravel your lie.

36:28.378 --> 36:29.177
In that case,

36:29.938 --> 36:32.097
Mr. Baraikin won't partner
with Shen Haoming,

36:32.617 --> 36:34.298
and Shen Haoming's promise
won't be kept.

36:34.617 --> 36:37.217
My offers will be withdrawn too.

36:38.298 --> 36:39.298
Ultimately,

36:39.657 --> 36:41.378
you'll gain nothing.

36:42.418 --> 36:43.257
Ms. Xu.

36:44.177 --> 36:45.018
Telling the truth

36:46.057 --> 36:47.018
isn't that hard.

36:48.338 --> 36:49.537
Just speak the truth.

36:51.057 --> 36:52.018
(I'll handle the rest.)

36:52.057 --> 36:52.617
Yan.

36:53.257 --> 36:53.818
Yan.

36:56.657 --> 36:57.617
Let me toast you.

36:59.217 --> 37:00.577
You look pale.

37:00.657 --> 37:01.657
Feeling unwell?

37:03.257 --> 37:03.858
Do I?

37:14.257 --> 37:16.137
Maybe I drank too quickly.

37:16.298 --> 37:17.217
Don't worry about me.

37:22.617 --> 37:24.458
Lemon water helps sober up.

37:25.858 --> 37:26.418
Thanks.

37:27.577 --> 37:30.418
Mr. Shen is a good husband.

37:34.498 --> 37:35.978
Your happy marriage

37:36.217 --> 37:37.617
is truly enviable.

37:38.378 --> 37:38.898
However,

37:39.418 --> 37:40.657
may I ask something?

37:41.737 --> 37:42.978
Ms. Xu, why are you not

37:43.418 --> 37:44.818
wearing your wedding ring?

37:52.657 --> 37:53.537
Wedding rings

37:54.097 --> 37:55.057
symbolize

37:55.057 --> 37:55.938
marital commitment.

37:56.298 --> 37:58.418
It explains the rumors

37:58.498 --> 37:59.338
about your divorce.

38:00.177 --> 38:01.778
If you're happy,

38:02.818 --> 38:04.418
why forget your wedding ring?

38:06.898 --> 38:07.778
Good point.

38:08.498 --> 38:09.137
See?

38:09.697 --> 38:12.097
This is my wedding ring.

38:12.498 --> 38:14.177
We bought it before our wedding.

38:14.537 --> 38:16.378
It's not very expensive,

38:16.418 --> 38:17.818
but I have been wearing it.

38:17.898 --> 38:19.338
It's priceless to me.

38:20.177 --> 38:21.217
Why is yours not on?

38:31.617 --> 38:32.858
In fact, I planned

38:33.177 --> 38:35.537
to make this trip

38:36.298 --> 38:38.217
to make it up to Yan.

38:43.097 --> 38:43.938
Our marriage

38:43.938 --> 38:45.458
has indeed encountered some issues.

38:49.818 --> 38:51.057
I wasn't mature enough.

38:52.458 --> 38:53.338
I did many things

38:53.737 --> 38:55.257
that hurt Yan deeply.

38:57.978 --> 38:59.458
A rift formed between us.

39:02.418 --> 39:03.418
We've been giving

39:04.432 --> 39:05.778
each other the silent treatment.

39:08.298 --> 39:09.577
During that time,

39:11.898 --> 39:13.577
memories of the past kept resurfacing.

39:18.898 --> 39:20.938
When I faced challenges at work,

39:22.697 --> 39:23.737
she stayed by my side,

39:24.458 --> 39:25.378
fighting alongside me.

39:30.537 --> 39:31.617
When someone tried

39:31.657 --> 39:33.097
to harm me,

39:34.938 --> 39:36.137
she didn't hesitate

39:36.938 --> 39:38.057
to shield me

39:39.818 --> 39:40.737
from any harm.

39:43.657 --> 39:44.938
When I focused on work

39:45.137 --> 39:46.177
and couldn't spare time,

39:47.858 --> 39:49.577
she lovingly cared for my parents

39:51.298 --> 39:52.338
and my brother.

39:54.577 --> 39:56.018
Her devotion to the family

39:58.378 --> 39:59.577
surpassed mine.

40:03.617 --> 40:04.898
During this time,

40:07.818 --> 40:08.737
I realized

40:10.378 --> 40:11.617
how deeply

40:12.818 --> 40:14.257
I miss her.

40:19.378 --> 40:20.498
And I came to know

40:22.418 --> 40:24.418
how crucial you are to me.

40:33.898 --> 40:35.257
I'd like both of you

40:35.498 --> 40:36.657
to witness this moment.

40:44.697 --> 40:45.697
Throughout this trip,

40:47.858 --> 40:49.378
I've carried this ring with me.

40:59.097 --> 41:00.458
Please forgive me

41:02.657 --> 41:04.217
and give me another chance. Will you?

41:11.057 --> 41:12.298
(Refuse if you want.)

41:13.858 --> 41:15.898
(I'll personally unravel your lie.)

41:17.737 --> 41:18.697
(In that case,)

41:19.257 --> 41:21.418
(Mr. Baraikin won't partner
with Shen Haoming,)

41:23.537 --> 41:25.257
(and Shen Haoming's promise
won't be kept.)

41:25.537 --> 41:28.177
(My offers will be withdrawn too.)

41:30.418 --> 41:31.378
(Ultimately,)

41:32.338 --> 41:34.018
(you'll gain nothing.)

41:41.577 --> 41:42.858
Don't let this happen again.

41:47.657 --> 41:48.378
Absolutely not.

41:51.546 --> 41:56.040
笙ｪI'm giving it all,
just getting nothing back笙ｪ

41:58.418 --> 42:00.177
Couples always have arguments,

42:01.097 --> 42:02.617
just like me and my wife.

42:03.097 --> 42:03.737
But

42:04.257 --> 42:05.097
we never

42:05.137 --> 42:06.938
let any misunderstanding

42:07.137 --> 42:08.498
truly separate us.

42:10.737 --> 42:12.737
I hope you'll reconcile completely.

42:13.577 --> 42:15.537
There's a Russian proverb,

42:16.137 --> 42:18.137
"Don't let the unchangeable past

42:18.537 --> 42:20.617
affect your present and future."

42:21.458 --> 42:22.577
Thank you for the advice.

42:23.257 --> 42:23.818
From now on,

42:24.177 --> 42:25.217
I'll strive to learn

42:25.938 --> 42:27.018
how to be a better husband

42:28.338 --> 42:29.737
and love my wife.

42:39.378 --> 42:40.018
Ms. Xu.

42:40.378 --> 42:42.458
If you've forgiven Mr. Shen,

42:42.978 --> 42:43.978
then

42:44.418 --> 42:45.858
shouldn't you kiss now?

43:12.537 --> 43:13.338
Excuse us.

43:18.097 --> 43:19.737
Our vacation ends tomorrow.

43:19.978 --> 43:21.097
We need to return early.

43:21.257 --> 43:22.617
Let's call it a day.

43:23.378 --> 43:24.298
Have a good rest.

43:24.418 --> 43:25.584
- We'll see you off.
- Okay.

43:25.818 --> 43:26.537
See you tomorrow.

43:26.818 --> 43:27.378
Dear.

43:27.737 --> 43:28.097
Bye.

43:28.378 --> 43:28.737
Bye.

43:33.898 --> 43:34.378
What?

43:34.498 --> 43:35.217
You stay.

43:35.577 --> 43:36.418
Bandage your wound.

43:36.458 --> 43:37.217
I can't drink.

43:37.818 --> 43:38.097
Stop.

43:38.097 --> 43:38.418
You can.

43:38.418 --> 43:39.338
Let's sit and talk.

43:39.338 --> 43:40.097
You were talkative.

43:40.577 --> 43:41.018
What?

43:41.097 --> 43:41.498
Sit.

43:41.978 --> 43:43.097
Let me redress your wound.

43:43.338 --> 43:43.617
Come.

44:01.577 --> 44:02.338
It looks lovely

44:02.378 --> 44:03.298
and suits you.

44:03.338 --> 44:04.938
I really like it.

44:05.898 --> 44:08.018
Having you here made my vacation

44:08.137 --> 44:09.537
truly joyful.

44:11.257 --> 44:13.378
Treasure each other dearly.

44:14.257 --> 44:15.338
Last night's kiss

44:15.617 --> 44:16.818
overflowed with genuine love.

44:16.858 --> 44:18.418
It clearly wasn't an act.

44:20.257 --> 44:21.577
Whenever you return home,

44:21.737 --> 44:22.537
do let me know.

44:23.257 --> 44:23.778
I will.

44:23.778 --> 44:24.858
We're friends now.

44:25.577 --> 44:26.338
Be safe.

44:26.657 --> 44:27.378
- See you.
- Next time,

44:27.778 --> 44:29.018
we must play golf together.

44:29.498 --> 44:29.978
Okay.

44:31.298 --> 44:31.978
Mr. Shen.

44:32.898 --> 44:34.458
I admire your composure.

44:34.898 --> 44:36.498
You've remained patient,

44:36.737 --> 44:38.737
never mentioning work matters.

44:39.498 --> 44:40.498
That's good.

44:41.778 --> 44:43.537
Since we met

44:43.577 --> 44:44.978
and got along so well,

44:45.537 --> 44:47.057
whatever your intention is,

44:47.177 --> 44:48.737
I'd love to hear about it.

44:50.378 --> 44:51.458
The vacation is over.

44:52.657 --> 44:53.818
Can you consider adding Jinda

44:53.978 --> 44:54.737
to the list

44:55.217 --> 44:56.898
for potential partners?

44:57.697 --> 44:58.858
I've heard

44:58.978 --> 45:00.018
Jinda is

45:00.018 --> 45:01.898
an excellent real estate company.

45:03.577 --> 45:04.737
I'll wait for your call.

45:05.577 --> 45:06.898
Don't forget our agreement.

45:07.177 --> 45:08.338
Whether you come to Russia

45:08.338 --> 45:09.577
or I visit China,

45:09.898 --> 45:11.737
we'll treat each other generously.

45:12.018 --> 45:12.537
Of course.

45:13.458 --> 45:14.057
Goodbye.

45:14.537 --> 45:15.057
Goodbye.

45:33.657 --> 45:34.257
Mr. Shen.

45:35.498 --> 45:36.938
I've completed my task.

45:37.978 --> 45:38.978
You did a great job.

45:40.137 --> 45:40.657
Alright then.

45:41.097 --> 45:42.057
I'll head back soon.

45:42.938 --> 45:43.600
I'll drive you.

45:48.978 --> 45:49.537
What's wrong?

45:59.537 --> 46:00.097
Sorry,

46:00.617 --> 46:01.904
I got used to holding your hand.

46:04.498 --> 46:05.737
You can change this habit.

46:10.938 --> 46:12.298
I'll take you home anyway.

46:18.554 --> 46:20.560
笙ｪLike fireworks that loved笙ｪ

46:20.560 --> 46:22.160
笙ｪRushing toward the stars笙ｪ

46:22.160 --> 46:24.942
笙ｪUndaunted by pain笙ｪ

46:25.232 --> 46:27.176
笙ｪFearless of flames笙ｪ

46:27.176 --> 46:31.856
笙ｪEven if just a fleeting sparkle笙ｪ

46:31.856 --> 46:33.680
笙ｪWe shed tears笙ｪ

46:33.680 --> 46:37.392
笙ｪDeep blue seas turn to foam笙ｪ

46:37.392 --> 46:41.347
笙ｪWe regained freedom笙ｪ

46:41.347 --> 46:43.952
笙ｪIf you remember me笙ｪ

46:43.952 --> 46:47.446
笙ｪThen I'm pleased笙ｪ

46:59.697 --> 47:03.841
笙ｪI just wanna take my time tonight笙ｪ

47:05.842 --> 47:10.132
笙ｪTo do all the things I said I'd try笙ｪ

47:11.857 --> 47:17.713
笙ｪI go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different place笙ｪ

47:18.193 --> 47:21.009
笙ｪI go drink, go party, and go dance笙ｪ

47:21.009 --> 47:24.337
笙ｪEven if I'm lonely笙ｪ

47:24.977 --> 47:29.713
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
too many times笙ｪ

47:31.485 --> 47:35.723
笙ｪI'm giving it all to get nothing back笙ｪ

47:37.585 --> 47:42.737
笙ｪI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see笙ｪ

47:43.825 --> 47:48.687
笙ｪSee the world and how it flows.
We never let go笙ｪ

47:50.417 --> 47:53.393
笙ｪSo I'll take my time笙ｪ

47:53.617 --> 47:56.785
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

47:56.785 --> 48:01.810
笙ｪThe love I should deserve笙ｪ

48:03.452 --> 48:06.458
笙ｪWhen the time is right笙ｪ

48:06.458 --> 48:09.735
笙ｪYou realize笙ｪ

48:09.735 --> 48:14.365
笙ｪIt will all be alright笙ｪ

